{"tid":1699431,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"罷工係咪唔返工然後喺屋企瞓覺就成功？","createTime":"2019-11-08T04:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T04:48:17.000Z","uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4b8a38a6f24d215b6b3f1b65938fc74338c363","tid":1699431,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:33:06.000Z","msg":"成日叫人罷工<br />\n罷工唔係問題呀<br />\n係咪唔返工留喺屋企瞓覺就有成效？<br />\n大佬你都要有集會有行動先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實要罷工有幾難<br />\n只係大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔知如果唔返工可以去邊</span></span></strong><br />\n真係就咁喺條街度企咩？<br />\n點解85咁成功？<br />\n唔只因為有宣傳<br />\n最重要有個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聚腳點</span></strong></span><br />\n當人一聚 一個影響一個 自自然然就人多<br />\n咁樣嘅罷工先有效<br />\n而唔係空口叫罷工就有用<br />\n一定要有行動集會先有動力去罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976754a282d3f43845ee34efeb90a1fcbc2ceb52","tid":1699431,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:48:17.000Z","msg":"有冇人諗法一樣<br />\n唔知如果唔返工可以去邊"}]}